Title: Greenish Roots Black Seed  Hair Oil
Description: Greenish Roots – Black Seed Hair Oil What is ‘Roots’ made of? Nigella Sativa – the wonder herb that is regarded as a panacea for all illnesses in the Arabian world, is the chief ingredient of our hair-oil. This Nigella oil, which is nothing less than the divine elixir, is made more potent by the addition of traditional Indian herbs that include hibiscus, amla, brahmi, fenugreek and henna. This powerful blend of herbs ensures that your hair strands get nourished from the root to the tip, resulting in dense and abundant hair-growth. It cures all scalp infections, and improves blood circulation by acting as a vaso-dilator. How does ‘Roots’ work? How it helps to combat hair-loss? ‘Roots’ hair oil aims to boost the anagenic phase while putting brakes on the categenic and telogenic phases. This desired result is achieved by deep penetration i.e. the oil seeps deep into the scalp and repairs the hair from its very roots. With prolonged use, even those hair follicles that have gone dormant are infused with new life and recover eventually. This may even produce new hairs on scalp that has started balding. ‘Roots’ hair oil boosts the growth of melanocytes i.e. cells that produce melanin, the pigment that lends the hair its characteristic black colour. This helps to check premature greying and the hair is restored to its natural colour. ‘Roots’ hair oil also heal the damaged keratinocytes – cells that act as a barrier against pathogens, UV radiation, heat and water loss, thereby producing luxuriant hair shafts. To make the long story short, ‘Roots’ hair oil is a complete hair-care solution, providing nourishment to the hair from the root to the tip  Directions for use:Apply 10 to 12ml of ‘Roots’ hair oil on clean scalp at night, leave on overnight, and rinse in the morning if desired. Alternatively, apply ‘Roots’ after bath in the morning and rinse off when required.For cases of severe hair-loss, apply twice daily.

Title: OMRON HJ 320AP Pedometer(White)
Description: Keeping fit is a rewarding experience, but you need a health device as a companion to actively monitor your every move. So, when every movement counts, you know that measuring your steps accurately cannot be done manually. For serving this purpose, the Omron Pedometer HJA-320 is devised. This health device is built with 3D Accelerometer Sensor which detects movement in three directions - vertically, horizontally and laterally.
